Backlight buttons for Hp 350 g2

Easiest solution is to download brghtness slider from app store allows you to map keys and places the app on tool bar 
next to the wifi.

or

Step 1: ioio by RehabMan https://bitbucket.org/RehabMan/os-x-ioio/downloads
Copy the binary 'ioio' to a directory in your path, such as /usr/bin

Step 2: Run this in Terminal
ioio -s ApplePS2Keyboard LogScanCodes 1

step 3: go utilities and open console.log app and find console.log

step 4: buttons pressed will appear keep note of them

step 5: remap 
